item.title: HTB Sherlock Brutus Writeup
item.description: Sherlock Scenario # In this very easy Sherlock, you will familiarize yourself with Unix auth.log and wtmp logs. We’ll explore a scenario where a Confluence server was brute-forced via its SSH service.
